# Cura

Use [UltiMaker Cura Support](https://support.ultimaker.com/hc/en-us/categories/360003567299-UltiMaker-Cura) as the reference for:

- **Printer Settings**: Machine config, extruder, build plate
- **Quality Settings**: Layer height, line width, walls, infill
- **Material Settings**: Temperatures, flow, retraction
- **Support**: Tree supports, brim, raft

Project layout:
- `slicer/cura/printer/` — printer definitions
- `slicer/cura/quality/` — quality presets
- `slicer/cura/material/` — material profiles
